   Climate index and mode information
     * Why and how do scientists study climate change in the Arctic? What
       are the Arctic Climate indices?
     * Research papers, impacts, trends and many other links to Climate
       Indices/Annular Modes information from Colorado State University
     * Pacific Decadal Oscillation (PDO)
     * Home Page for material relating to possible post-1977 regime shift
     * North Pacific Interdecadal Climate Variability and Oceanic
       Ecosystem Response
     * Air temperature/Precipitation variability characterized by
       trends/regressions onto ENSO, AO, PDO, from the University of
       Washington
     * North Pacific Climate Variability
     * Arctic Oscillation
     * Pacific Decadal Oscillation explanation from NASA/JPL

